<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Tactic — Event Planning</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;0,700;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/index.css">
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
    <div class="nav-inner">
        <div class="logo">Tac<span>tic</span></div>
        <div class="nav-links">
            <a href="#events">Events</a>
            <a href="#vendors">Vendors</a>
            <a href="#testimonials">Reviews</a>
            <a href="auth.html" class="nav-btn">Get Started</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-glow g1"></div>
    <div class="hero-glow g2"></div>
    <div class="hero-glow g3"></div>
    <div class="hero-content">
        <p class="hero-eyebrow">Your event. Your moment.</p>
        <h1>Plan every detail.<br><span>Stress about none.</span></h1>
        <p class="hero-sub">Tactic brings together venues, caterers, entertainers, and more — all in one place, built for the moments that matter most.</p>
        <div class="hero-btns">
            <a href="auth.html" class="btn-primary">Start planning →</a>
            <a href="#events" class="btn-ghost">See what we support</a>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-stats">
            <div class="stat"><span>500+</span><p>Vendors</p></div>
            <div class="stat-divider"></div>
            <div class="stat"><span>12K+</span><p>Events planned</p></div>
            <div class="stat-divider"></div>
            <div class="stat"><span>98%</span><p>Happy hosts</p></div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- EVENT TYPES -->
<section class="section" id="events">
    <div class="section-inner">
        <p class="section-label">What we support</p>
        <h2>Every occasion,<br>covered.</h2>
        <p class="section-sub">From intimate birthdays to grand weddings, Tactic has the tools and vendors for every kind of celebration.</p>
        <div class="event-grid">
            <div class="event-card">
                <div class="event-icon">🎂</div>
                <h3>Birthdays</h3>
                <p>Make every year count with curated vendors, custom invites, and a seamless guest experience.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="event-card featured">
                <div class="event-badge">Most popular</div>
                <div class="event-icon">💍</div>
                <h3>Weddings</h3>
                <p>Your perfect day deserves perfect planning. Venues, florists, caterers, and more — one dashboard.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="event-card">
                <div class="event-icon">🎉</div>
                <h3>House Parties</h3>
                <p>Keep it casual without compromising on quality. DJs, decorators, and food — sorted in minutes.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="event-card">
                <div class="event-icon">🤝</div>
                <h3>Corporate</h3>
                <p>Professional events that leave an impression. Conference venues, catering, and entertainment on demand.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="event-card">
                <div class="event-icon">🎶</div>
                <h3>Social Gatherings</h3>
                <p>Reunions, get-togethers, or just because — Tactic handles the details so you enjoy the moment.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="event-card">
                <div class="event-icon">✨</div>
                <h3>And more</h3>
                <p>Whatever you're celebrating, Tactic is flexible enough to handle it your way.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- VENDORS -->
<section class="section alt" id="vendors">
    <div class="section-inner">
        <p class="section-label">Our vendors</p>
        <h2>The best people<br>for the job.</h2>
        <p class="section-sub">Every vendor on Tactic is verified and reviewed, so you can book with confidence.</p>
        <div class="vendor-grid">
            <div class="vendor-card">
                <div class="vendor-img" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b1f6e, #7c3aed);">🏛️</div>
                <div class="vendor-info">
                    <div class="vendor-meta">
                        <span class="vendor-category">Venue</span>
                        <span class="vendor-rating">★ 4.9</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Coco Lawns</h3>
                    <p>Miramar, Goa</p>
                    <p class="vendor-price">From ₹50,000</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="vendor-card">
                <div class="vendor-img" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a3a5c, #2563eb);">🍽️</div>
                <div class="vendor-info">
                    <div class="vendor-meta">
                        <span class="vendor-category">Caterer</span>
                        <span class="vendor-rating">★ 4.8</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Spice Route Catering</h3>
                    <p>Panaji, Goa</p>
                    <p class="vendor-price">From ₹800/head</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="vendor-card">
                <div class="vendor-img" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3d1a1a, #dc2626);">🎵</div>
                <div class="vendor-info">
                    <div class="vendor-meta">
                        <span class="vendor-category">DJ</span>
                        <span class="vendor-rating">★ 4.7</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3>DJ Raven</h3>
                    <p>Calangute, Goa</p>
                    <p class="vendor-price">From ₹15,000</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="vendor-card">
                <div class="vendor-img" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a3d2b, #16a34a);">🌸</div>
                <div class="vendor-info">
                    <div class="vendor-meta">
                        <span class="vendor-category">Florist</span>
                        <span class="vendor-rating">★ 4.9</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Bloom & Co.</h3>
                    <p>Mapusa, Goa</p>
                    <p class="vendor-price">From ₹5,000</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- TESTIMONIALS -->
<section class="section" id="testimonials">
    <div class="section-inner">
        <p class="section-label">What people say</p>
        <h2>Hosts who trusted<br>Tactic.</h2>
        <div class="testimonial-grid">
            <div class="testimonial-card">
                <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
                <p>"Tactic made planning my wedding feel like the easiest thing in the world. Every vendor was professional and everything went perfectly."</p>
                <div class="testimonial-author">
                    <div class="author-avatar">P</div>
                    <div>
                        <strong>Priya Menon</strong>
                        <span>Wedding · Goa</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial-card featured">
                <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
                <p>"I planned my entire birthday party in under an hour. The vendor booking system is brilliant — confirmed, done, sorted."</p>
                <div class="testimonial-author">
                    <div class="author-avatar">R</div>
                    <div>
                        <strong>Rohan D'Souza</strong>
                        <span>Birthday · Goa</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial-card">
                <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
                <p>"Our annual corporate event has never been this smooth. Tactic handled everything from venue to catering without a single hitch."</p>
                <div class="testimonial-author">
                    <div class="author-avatar">A</div>
                    <div>
                        <strong>Asha Kamat</strong>
                        <span>Corporate · Goa</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA -->
<section class="cta-section">
    <div class="hero-glow g1" style="top: 0; left: 30%;"></div>
    <div class="cta-inner">
        <p class="section-label">Ready to begin?</p>
        <h2>Your next event<br>starts here.</h2>
        <p>Join thousands of hosts who plan smarter with Tactic. It's free to get started.</p>
        <a href="auth.html" class="btn-primary large">Create your event →</a>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- FOOTER -->
<footer>
    <div class="footer-inner">
        <div class="logo">Tac<span>tic</span></div>
        <p>One tick closer to your big moment.</p>
        <p class="footer-copy">© 2026 Tactic. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
